    "description": "RML Hospital Holdings Services, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Surgeon for our Kochi operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout RML Hospital Holdings Services:\nRML Hospital Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with RML Hospital Holdings Services!",
